    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902870/extras/09aabf2cea55439c093c1c4b7b55b607.avif?t=1729108584\" width=589 height=78 /></span><br><br>在 Vertical Kingdom 中，横跨一整代人的战争摧毁了这个世界。曾经伟大的帝国现已满目疮痍，就看伟大建筑师如何一砖一瓦地重现它昔日的辉煌。游历这片土地，踏上随机的“类 Rogue”征途。利用基于卡牌的全新建筑系统，同时考虑复杂的资源经济，才能建造新的城市。<br><br>重建帝国，不是通过武力或狡诈的政治斗争，而是通过砖块和泥浆!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902870/extras/789260f2d3a09f73e556f223f7b9641f.poster.avif?t=1729108584\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902870/extras/789260f2d3a09f73e556f223f7b9641f.webm?t=1729108584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902870/extras/789260f2d3a09f73e556f223f7b9641f.mp4?t=1729108584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902870/extras/1be53097c93f4c49f394a685b00c4b56.avif?t=1729108584\" width=589 height=78 /></span><br><br>使用基于卡牌的系统建造高耸的城市。每一回合挑选五副牌，靠打牌来向上建造。管理食物、水、砖、木材、石头和金属等资源，需要这些来确保城市有发展空间并打出新牌。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902870/extras/aa5a813b42c22f1b77a48f50c5013685.poster.avif?t=1729108584\" width=600 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902870/extras/aa5a813b42c22f1b77a48f50c5013685.webm?t=1729108584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902870/extras/aa5a813b42c22f1b77a48f50c5013685.mp4?t=1729108584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902870/extras/3e47631d42d8f28b1f7307f064e344f7.avif?t=1729108584\" width=589 height=78 /></span><br><br>作为伟大建筑师，你的工作是重建帝国，一次一个建筑，一次一片地区。进行伟大的远征，以皇帝的名义建造新的城市，并应对每个地区的挑战：险恶的地形，资源短缺，以及永远受限的建造空间。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902870/extras/da5f0659b6f581d780da6f1a9768f932.poster.avif?t=1729108584\" width=600 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902870/extras/da5f0659b6f581d780da6f1a9768f932.webm?t=1729108584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902870/extras/da5f0659b6f581d780da6f1a9768f932.mp4?t=1729108584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902870/extras/318f869dea5329f23b52c4d533198bd5.avif?t=1729108584\" width=589 height=78 /></span><br><br>请谨慎做每个决定、打每张牌，因为建筑建好了就永远存在，不能推倒重来。在公民住所和生产场所之间做好规划，使它们互相配合，发挥更大作用。带来更多的税收、资源，并使公民对帝国保持忠诚——也许当地人会帮助你对付潜伏在废墟中的邪恶之物……<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902870/extras/9975d26536f994ad2a00f46f1a527232.poster.avif?t=1729108584\" width=600 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902870/extras/9975d26536f994ad2a00f46f1a527232.webm?t=1729108584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902870/extras/9975d26536f994ad2a00f46f1a527232.mp4?t=1729108584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
